ghost-role-information-n14pet-eyebot-tribe-name = Tribal Eyebot Companion
ghost-role-information-n14pet-eyebot-tribe-description =
    You are a follower of someone, obey them and attempt to protect them. In-case they perish you may continue to serve the tribe.
    You have a knife strapped onto your chassis, which others can apply reagents onto. Be careful entering melee though, as you're quite fragile!
